        "TileImage": "$($repository 5d66981e-2ced-499c-9330-3e0bfd4688b3).Image",
        "Description": "This&apos;ll bring back old memories. Your primary target is Leo Collins, a security guard working at Vinedo Yates in Argentina. It seems as if he arranged a wedding for his friend, Kolten Case. We have arrived late and most of the guests have left, but your two targets are still here. Our client, Kolten Case&apos;s wife, has soon realized that both Leo Collins and Kolten Case were involved in a massive drug trafficking scandal. She has hired you to take them both down. It&apos;s Mississipi all over again...",
